languages.text: Однако ксеносы не отвечают на входящие сигналы. Спустя несколько попыток настроенная Мастером вокса частота сбивается, и горестная песнь затихает.
However, the xenos do not respond to the incoming signals. After several attempts, the frequency tuned by the Vox Master gets lost, and the mournful song fades away.

languages.text: 然而，异形并没有回应发过去的信息。几次尝试之后，音阵大师同步的频率丢失了，哀伤的歌声也随之消失。
languages.original_text: However, the xenos do not respond to the incoming signals. After several attempts, the frequency tuned by the Vox Master gets lost, and the mournful song fades away.

traits.locale_text: 然而，异形并没有回应发过去的信息。几次尝试之后，音阵大师同步的频率丢失了，哀伤的歌声也随之消失。

languages.text: しかし、異種族は受信信号に反応しない。何度か試みたが、ヴォクス・マスターが調整した周波数は失われ、悲痛な歌声は消えていった。
languages.original_text: However, the xenos do not respond to the incoming signals. After several attempts, the frequency tuned by the Vox Master gets lost, and the mournful song fades away.

traits.locale_text: しかし、異種族は受信信号に反応しない。何度か試みたが、ヴォクス・マスターが調整した周波数は失われ、悲痛な歌声は消えていった。

languages.text: Sin embargo, los xenos no responden a las señales entrantes. Tras varios intentos, la frecuencia sintonizada por la maestra de vocos se pierde, y la lúgubre canción se desvanece.
languages.original_text: However, the xenos do not respond to the incoming signals. After several attempts, the frequency tuned by the Vox Master gets lost, and the mournful song fades away.

traits.locale_text: Sin embargo, los xenos no responden a las señales entrantes. Tras varios intentos, la frecuencia sintonizada por la maestra de vocos se pierde, y la lúgubre canción se desvanece.

languages.text: Doch die Xenos reagieren nicht auf die eingehenden Signale. Nach mehreren Versuchen verschwindet die von der Voxmeisterin kalibrierte Frequenz und das traurige Lied verklingt.
languages.original_text: However, the xenos do not respond to the incoming signals. After several attempts, the frequency tuned by the Vox Master gets lost, and the mournful song fades away.

traits.locale_text: Doch die Xenos reagieren nicht auf die eingehenden Signale. Nach mehreren Versuchen verschwindet die von der Voxmeisterin kalibrierte Frequenz und das traurige Lied verklingt.

languages.text: Cependant, les xénos ne répondent pas à leurs appels répétés. Après plusieurs tentatives, la connexion établie par la maîtresse-vox est coupée et le chant funèbre se tait.

languages.text: Ne var ki zenolar, gelen sinyallere yanıt vermiyor. Birkaç denemenin ardından Voks Üstadı'nın ayarladığı frekansın kaybolmasıyla hüzünlü şarkı da azalarak son buluyor.
